Shift + Del -> delete a line
Shift+ F6 -> Refactor/Rename

Ctrl + ` -> change theme (overridden by Ditto!)
Ctrl + L -> search
Ctrl + D -> duplicate line
Ctrl + Q -> Shows info about the function !

Ctrl + Shift + k -> commit and push
Ctrl + Shift + a -> find in options

Ctrl + Alt + L -> Auto formats the code!
Ctrl + Alt + M -> Extract method

Alt + Enter -> add/import libraries
